title: Car wash equipment US-DG-luxury
short_description:
DG LUXURY CAR WASHING EQUIPMENT.

FUNCTONS:

  • 1. Without chassis wash.
  • 2. Shampoo A and shampoo B system.
  • 3. High pressure two sides washing and top profile washing.
  • 4. Automatic profile drying system.
  • 5. Wheel washing brushes.
short_description_uz:
DG LUXURY AVTOMOBIL YUVISH USKUNASI.

FUNKSIYALARI:

  • 1. Shassidan tashqari qismlarni yuvishi mumkin.
  • 2. Shampun A va shampun B dasturli yuvish tizimiga ega.
  • 3. Ikki tomon va yuqori profilni yuvishning yuqori bosimli tizimi mavjud.
  • 4. Profilni quritishning avtomatik tizimiga ega.
  • 5. G'ildiraklarni yuvish uchun maxsus cho'tkalari mavjud.
short_description_ru:
DG LUXURY АВТОМОЙКА.
